<use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bzg1665702547028.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bzg1665702547028.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bzg1665702547028.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bzg1665702547028\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bzg1665702547028___proxy_settings__450394\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the [PROXY_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to configure a proxy server for use by the UHTTP component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bzg1665702547028__topic_d138563e1_d138564e1_d138565e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1063631e52\">Syntax</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzg1665702547028__p_d138569e1_d138570e1_d138571e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">[PROXY_SETTINGS]</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Setting</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var></p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bzg1665702547028__p_d138572e1_d138573e1_d138574e1\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bzg1665702547028__pre_c5m_jbp_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[PROXY_SETTINGS]\n$SERVER = http://www.proxy-server.company.com:8001\n$UHTTP_DEF_PROXY_AUTH = BL\n$BYPASS = www.mycompany.com\n$DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY = 1\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bzg1665702547028__topic_d98572e1_d98573e1_d98574e1_d98575e1_d98576e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1063631e80\">\n                       \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bzg1665702547028__li_d48872e1_d48873e1_d48874e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Setting</var>—name of the proxy setting. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bzg1665702547028__li_d48875e1_d48876e1_d48877e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var> is the value of the setting.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example assignment file specifies a number of proxy settings:</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"bzg1665702547028__note_w2269ab1b5b7b5b3_w2270ab1b5b7b5_w2271ab1b5b7_w2272ab1b5_w2273ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY</span> is relevant only for Microsoft Windows\n               platforms.</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526325\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526325\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[PROXY_SETTINGS] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Use the [PROXY_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to configure a proxy server for use by the UHTTP component. Syntax [PROXY_SETTINGS] Setting { = } Value For example: [PROXY_SETTINGS] $SERVER = http://www.proxy-server.company.com:8001 $UHTTP_DEF_PROXY_AUTH = BL $BYPASS = www.mycompany.com $DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY = 1 Copy Arguments Setting —name of the proxy setting. Value is the value of the setting. The following example assignment file specifies a number of proxy settings: Note: $DO_NOT_USE_REGISTRY is relevant only for Microsoft Windows platforms. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}